cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.NE 

The paper discusses deep learning techniques for natural language processing (NLP), specifically for emotion analysis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also discusses the use of pre-trained word embeddings, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also mentions the use of convolutional neural networks (cs.CV) and neural networks (cs.NE) for the emotion analysis task.
